  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game uses two styles.2D and 3D　are Used.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To clear the game, you need to go through various stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The stages that will appear include the following Shrines, abandoned houses, highways, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each stage has different actions to advance to the next stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to shoot a gun to defeat the enemy, or you can't. Sometimes there is no other way but to just run away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371030/extras/8b78e041cc9eff56855b85d87f814b80.avif?t=1736360960\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371030/extras_big/8b78e041cc9eff56855b85d87f814b80.avif?t=1736360960 width=800 height=1130 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game uses two styles.2D and 3D　are Used.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To clear the game, you need to go through various stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The stages that will appear include the following Shrines, abandoned houses, highways, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each stage has different actions to advance to the next stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to shoot a gun to defeat the enemy, or you can't. Sometimes there is no other way but to just run away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371030/extras/8b78e041cc9eff56855b85d87f814b80.avif?t=1736360960\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371030/extras_big/8b78e041cc9eff56855b85d87f814b80.avif?t=1736360960 width=800 height=1130 /></span></p>",
